  "detailed_description": "King of Stocks is an engaging and enjoyable stock trading simulation game. In this game, you'll take on the role of an investor, aiming to profit by buying and selling stocks. You can choose from a variety of stocks to trade and capitalize on market fluctuations to earn the price difference. Through continuous practice, you'll gradually become a stock market tycoon, achieving success in the world of stock trading.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keep an eye on market trends</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016810/extras/0c0f8bd0a97fed6ba53f9226895abd1f.poster.avif?t=1736998109\" width=300 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016810/extras/0c0f8bd0a97fed6ba53f9226895abd1f.webm?t=1736998109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016810/extras/0c0f8bd0a97fed6ba53f9226895abd1f.mp4?t=1736998109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make wise decisions based on trends<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stay informed about market rumors</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016810/extras/ebd1607c6fb45abfcecf623d48402c47.avif?t=1736998109\" width=300 height=179 /></span><br>Rumors may be false; whether to believe them or not is up to you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Obtain new appearances</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016810/extras/cbed99f84148ae7b0bf650c8f28b66a9.avif?t=1736998109\" width=300 height=178 /></span><br>Unlock 10 new appearances based on total assets, with increasing difficulty.",
